description.narrative: Following the 2013 Education Review Office reviews of the three schools in Tokelau, the village and national councils of Tokelau agreed to a programme of improvements to teaching and learning, and school management and governance. Massey University was contracted in 2014 to provide this support. ERO reviewed progress in early 2018.
